{
  "texts": [
    "It's also more complicated to choose a large-scale agile framework.",
    "The study in [14] claims that while various agile frameworks provide basic understandings, they soon become unhelpful when applied outside of the context of the framework in which they were designed.",
    "Due to the COVID-19 epidemic, there has been an increase in remote project work globally.",
    "Working on remote projects offers its own set of difficulties [13].",
    "Based on research conducted by [15] on self-organizing teams, the challenges at the project, team, person, and task levels are categorized."
  ]
}